author: Paul Cullen, Jack Horgan-Jones
title: Coronavirus: Death rate from virus in Ireland rises to 2.4%
description: It will take 10 days to reach testing goal, Minister says
content:
The death rate from Covid-19 in the State has risen to 2.4 per cent, a new report shows, as the disease takes a further toll on vulnerable groups.
